{"tid":1812642,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"塔羅牌解讀籌款 所有收益捐至澳洲山火","createTime":"2020-01-05T15:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T00:38:06.000Z","uid":331712,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fa5a5ffb3d9ce6db9b219dcebb84904c6784429f","tid":1812642,"uid":331712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T15:42:35.000Z","msg":"我係素人塔羅師 希望為澳洲山火既受害者籌款 <br />\n<br />\n網站：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.communityenterprisefoundation.com.au/make-a-donation/bushfire-disaster-appeal/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.communityenterprisefoundation.com.au%2Fmake-a-donation%2Fbushfire-disaster-appeal%2F&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1dOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=c7fefcb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.communityenterprisefoundation.com.au/make-a-donation/bushfire-disaster-appeal/</a><br />\n<br />\n本人大約有100小時塔羅牌訓練 因為無自己既品牌/網站 未有資格出去擺檔 唯有用依種方法去籌款 <br />\n<br />\n初步想先幫人占 然後大家隨心捐錢 跟住截圖up返上來 有5個人無up相我就暫停活動 大家覺得依個方法可行嗎<br />\n<br />\n另外歡迎提出更好捐款機構/募捐辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可行正皮<br />\n唔可行負皮"},{"pid":"be96470686a58834e3e9fb4d5827a21ba3e33c2f","tid":1812642,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T15:47:35.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"d8befc6524f8aed48462430ccd17c353998ee2f8","tid":1812642,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T15:47:53.000Z","msg":"都係表示一個心意"},{"pid":"c0bb24d90da4157379e6c8920b3ba63297e1f80e","tid":1812642,"uid":71509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T15:49:06.000Z","msg":"唔係話唔好<br />\n<br />\n不過好多手足仲要幫 <br />\n<br />\n手足唔係condom"},{"pid":"1baa3c58b922039ecbbb33ec46dfc62b952bb3f9","tid":1812642,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T16:01:23.000Z","msg":"用香港人身份捐助亦都係公關手法嘅一種未嘗不可"},{"pid":"5188d6ace05fcc73ae5522665c3f05ac8ee6c87a","tid":1812642,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":